title: Abort or Cancel a Jenkins Pipeline From Jenkinsfile
tags: @zettel _method jenkins
roam-id: 55de2e82-d082-431b-b223-a0d9d0a0d4b9
type: text/markdown

``` groovy
pipeline {
  agent none

  environment {
    A = "abc"
  }

  stages {
    stage("conditional stage") {
      steps {
        script {
          if ( A == "abc" ) {
            error "aborting the pipeline"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
